text: Jessica Faye Gunning (born 21 May 1986) is an English actress. She has appeared in the TV series White Heat (2012), What Remains (2013), Back (2017–2021), and The Outlaws (2021–2024). Gunning became well known for her role as Martha Scott in Baby Reindeer (2024). She won a Primetime Emmy Award and a Golden Globe Award for this role.
